About Velixo

With close to 3,300 customers globally, Velixo is a leading Excel-based software company specializing in developing reporting, budgeting, data and template solutions for various ERP software such as Acumatica, Sage Intacct, and Microsoft Dynamics 365 Business Central. We provide advanced yet simple-to-use reporting tools that empower businesses to gain valuable insights, become more efficient, and automate processes from and to their ERP data.

About The Role

We are looking for a passionate ERP Data Analyst to join our team at Velixo. As an ERP Data Analyst, you will be responsible for demonstrating product capabilities, analyzing business requirements, and designing reporting solutions using SQL and Excel. Your expertise in Microsoft Excel, strong analytical mindset, and ability to provide valuable insights will play a crucial role in helping our customers leverage our Excel-based reporting solution for their ERP systems. This is an exciting opportunity to work in the ERP software industry and be part of a collaborative and growth-oriented team. We are considering candidates anywhere in Australia or New Zealand.

Responsibilities: 

Attend virtual product demonstrations with prospective customers, answer technical questions and demonstrate complex functionalities. 
Create proof-of-concept to highlight Velixo capabilities to prospective customers. 
